oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.visualInformationBuilder.businessRules.publicCommon.core.testUtils
Class RuleParser

java.lang.Object
  oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.visualInformationBuilder.businessRules.publicCommon.core.testUtils.RuleParser

public class RuleParser
extends java.lang.Object

Utility class to generate BusinessRules Rule Grammar : Clause blocks IF { } DO { } Clause blocks are linked by THEN or ELSE statements Ex: IF { } THEN { DO { } THEN { DO { } } } ELSE { IF { } THEN { DO { } } } Condition : for unittesting, we will use very simple fake conditions defined with only 1 character Connectives : & , | Nested : () UserDefined : [] Selected : * ex : (A&[B*|C&]) Example of a full rule : IF { (A&[B*|C&] |)& } THEN { DO { D&E& } } ELSE { DO { F& } } ex : Rule : IF{A&B|C|}THEN{DO{E&F&G&}}ELSE{DO{H&I&J&}} gives IF{C|>>>}THEN{DO{>}}ELSE{DO{>}}
